</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Apple 或研發摺疊型 MacBook   萬物皆可摺疊機</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/26/report-apple-exploring-20-inch-all-screen-foldable-macbook-but-foldable-iphone-delayed-until-2025/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=report-apple-exploring-20-inch-all-screen-foldable-macbook-but-foldable-iphone-delayed-until-2025</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 26 Feb 2022 05:02:04 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[Fold]]></category><category><![CDATA[macbook]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087347</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>摺疊機風潮近年越發普及，不少手機品牌紛紛推出摺疊機迎合趨勢，早前更有 Apple 已準備好推出摺疊型 iPho [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">摺疊機風潮近年越發普及，不少手機品牌紛紛推出摺疊機迎合趨勢，早前更有 Apple 已準備好推出摺疊型 iPhone 的傳言。最近有外國組織表示，預測 Apple 的摺疊型 iPhone 將在 2023 年至 2024 年問世；令人震驚的是，他們認為 Apple 將推出折疊螢幕的 Macbook，攤開後可看到相當於 20 吋的顯示面積。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/C2726BA7-5F3A-4C2A-97E5-EBACC77E60D4-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/C2726BA7-5F3A-4C2A-97E5-EBACC77E60D4-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/C2726BA7-5F3A-4C2A-97E5-EBACC77E60D4-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/C2726BA7-5F3A-4C2A-97E5-EBACC77E60D4-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/C2726BA7-5F3A-4C2A-97E5-EBACC77E60D4-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/C2726BA7-5F3A-4C2A-97E5-EBACC77E60D4.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Display Supply Chain Consultants（DSCC）日前表示，認為 Apple 將推出摺疊螢幕的 Macbook。該產品將具有 20 吋的顯示面積，如果對半摺疊，意味著產品本身相當於常見的 11 至 12 吋機型。DSCC 執行長 Ross Young 認為，Apple 可能預設這個產品有兩種使用情境，一種是具備全尺吋觸控螢幕鍵盤的筆記型電腦模式；另一種則是展開後與鍵盤滑鼠一同使用的顯示器。而顯示器的解析度，目前據稱將會以 4K 為目標。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ross Young 表示，可摺疊的 MacBook 在 2026 年，或 2027 年才有可能推出。此外，他先前曾預告今年出的 iPhone 14 Pro 前鏡頭改為挖孔設計，取代以往大家嫌棄的瀏海外型，就看之後的發表會是否如他所言成真。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/02/21/apple-exploring-20-inch-foldable-macbook/">MacRumors</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Gzpmg8L7Tvs:A39deuD84eI:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Gzpmg8L7Tvs:A39deuD84eI:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>俄國記者於烏克蘭遇無人機炮擊，砲彈於距離其 10 米處爆炸險喪命</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/26/journalists-in-ukraine-were-hit-by-drone-fire-just-10-meters-from-the-blast-site/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=journalists-in-ukraine-were-hit-by-drone-fire-just-10-meters-from-the-blast-site</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 26 Feb 2022 05:00:52 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[俄羅斯]]></category><category><![CDATA[烏克蘭]]></category><category><![CDATA[砲擊]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087782</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>俄羅斯與烏克蘭局勢持續升溫，俄羅斯方已展開軍事行動，在烏克蘭首都基輔投下導彈，多處地方傳出爆炸聲。一名俄羅斯記 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">俄羅斯與烏克蘭局勢持續升溫，俄羅斯方已展開軍事行動，在烏克蘭首都基輔投下導彈，多處地方傳出爆炸聲。一名俄羅斯記者 23 日在分離主義地區頓涅茨克（Donetsk）地區進行拍攝時，遇上無人機砲擊，砲彈最後落於距離他 10 米處爆炸，險些喪命。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1087783 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D05E9C63-71D6-4F78-A145-02FFC27C9725-694x384.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D05E9C63-71D6-4F78-A145-02FFC27C9725-694x384.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D05E9C63-71D6-4F78-A145-02FFC27C9725-1280x708.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D05E9C63-71D6-4F78-A145-02FFC27C9725-768x425.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D05E9C63-71D6-4F78-A145-02FFC27C9725-1536x850.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D05E9C63-71D6-4F78-A145-02FFC27C9725-2048x1133.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D05E9C63-71D6-4F78-A145-02FFC27C9725.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">俄羅斯紅星電視台一名戰地記者日前到頓涅茨克郊區，打算採訪沒有撤離衝突地區的居民，不料受到意外砲擊，鏡頭亦記錄了當時情況。影片中可見，該名男記者在報導時一直往後退，旁邊的士兵突然提醒，不出數秒便發生砲擊。記者身後發生爆炸冒出黑色煙霧，採訪人員與士兵迅速躲在旁邊有遮蔽物的地方避難。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1087784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/5948C186-7E0A-4DB6-B38F-78CEC3C17132.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="441" /></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;">其後據俄羅斯媒體報導，未獲廣泛承認的頓內茨克人民共和國（DPR）民兵發言人示，這名記者是遭到烏克蘭政府軍第 56 機動步兵旅的砲擊，但相關細節仍在調查中；隨行的頓內茨克分離主義軍人亦認為，是一架烏克蘭的無人機空投了一枚迫擊砲彈。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">該名記者其後在 Twitter 上發文「報平安」，表示自己暫時脫離危險，「這裡目前仍然有砲擊，我和同事都會照顧自己，當地局勢雖然是危險的，不過大家仍努力照常工作，假裝好像沒有戰爭一樣，我真不敢相信會發生這些事」。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">There is still shelling going on around here. I’m taking care of my colleagues and myself. Situation is dynamic and dangerous. People are still going to work and acting like this isn’t a war. I can’t believe what is happening here. Fuck.</p><p>&mdash; Bryce Wilson (@brycewilsonAU) <a href="https://twitter.com/brycewilsonAU/status/1496734837666992131?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 24, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/zvezdanews/status/1496518503003828224">Twitter</a>、Reuters</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=RHXPkpXUHSE:kf9yprN4Kh4:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=RHXPkpXUHSE:kf9yprN4Kh4:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>OpenSea 受黑客攻擊損失 2337 萬  NFT  交易量一週減 37%</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/26/recent-opensea-nft-heist-reduces-the-platforms-trading-activity-by-37/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=recent-opensea-nft-heist-reduces-the-platforms-trading-activity-by-37</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 26 Feb 2022 05:00:09 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[NFT]]></category><category><![CDATA[OpenSea]]></category><category><![CDATA[黑客]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087777</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>全球最大 NFT 市場 OpenSea 早前公佈至少 32 名用戶遭受釣魚電郵攻擊，損失總值約 300 萬美元 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">全球最大 NFT 市場 OpenSea 早前公佈至少 32 名用戶遭受釣魚電郵攻擊，損失總值約 300 萬美元（約 2337 萬港元）的 NFT（非同質代幣）。據數據顯示，OpenSea 受黑客攻擊後交易量下降了 37%。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0FEFD170-5943-4D5C-AF90-ECCDDB9DECCB-694x540.png" alt="" width="694" height="540" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0FEFD170-5943-4D5C-AF90-ECCDDB9DECCB-694x540.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0FEFD170-5943-4D5C-AF90-ECCDDB9DECCB-768x597.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/0FEFD170-5943-4D5C-AF90-ECCDDB9DECCB.png 1157w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據報導，早前一名匿名黑客通過分享惡意電子郵件，表示用戶可以將自己的以太幣放盤遷移到新的智能合約，從最大的 NFT 市場 OpenSea 竊取了至少 254 個代幣。 當中至少有 32 個用戶在這次攻擊中在惡意內容 (payload) 中署名。OpenSea 的首席執行官表示，被盜代幣的總價值為 170 萬美元，但獨立研究人員表示，黑客造成的實際損失可能在 200 萬美元到 300 萬美元之間。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">經此事件，OpenSea 上的用戶活動迅速下降，近 7 日交易量下降了 37%。NFT 社區介入后，大量用戶表示要離開 OpenSea。過去 7 天 OpenSea 交易者數量下降 19%，至約 227272 人。而在 2 月 20 日至 2 月 23 日期間，OpenSea 競爭對手 LooksRare 平臺的交易額從 500 萬美元增至 2500 萬美元。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://crypto.news/opensea-nft-platform-trading-activity-37/">Crypto News</a>、OpenSea</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Au_wA-xzvnk:dz_2RDOLMjo:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Au_wA-xzvnk:dz_2RDOLMjo:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Toyota 推出 2022 ALL NEW NOAH   安全性、舒適度全面升級</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/26/toyota-2022-all-new-noah/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=toyota-2022-all-new-noah</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 26 Feb 2022 05:00:05 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[All New Noah]]></category><category><![CDATA[Noah]]></category><category><![CDATA[Toyota]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087930</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>2022 年多間車廠都相繼推出不同新車型，日本車廠 Toyota 亦不甘落後，推出豐田 ALL NEW NOA [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">2022 年多間車廠都相繼推出不同新車型，日本車廠 Toyota 亦不甘落後，推出豐田 ALL NEW NOAH，實現「MORE」全方位升級概念，提供七座 Luxury 豪華版和八座 Advantage 優越版以供選擇。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D13FEE0-0EAC-4249-B22C-B3B8030551B7-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D13FEE0-0EAC-4249-B22C-B3B8030551B7-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D13FEE0-0EAC-4249-B22C-B3B8030551B7-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D13FEE0-0EAC-4249-B22C-B3B8030551B7-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D13FEE0-0EAC-4249-B22C-B3B8030551B7-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D13FEE0-0EAC-4249-B22C-B3B8030551B7-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6D13FEE0-0EAC-4249-B22C-B3B8030551B7-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/84381D83-7946-4021-8B17-F445FECEF8FC-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/84381D83-7946-4021-8B17-F445FECEF8FC-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/84381D83-7946-4021-8B17-F445FECEF8FC-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/84381D83-7946-4021-8B17-F445FECEF8FC-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/84381D83-7946-4021-8B17-F445FECEF8FC-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/84381D83-7946-4021-8B17-F445FECEF8FC-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/84381D83-7946-4021-8B17-F445FECEF8FC-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D9EF3DE9-DE5B-42C7-96EC-FB247A671E9F-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D9EF3DE9-DE5B-42C7-96EC-FB247A671E9F-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D9EF3DE9-DE5B-42C7-96EC-FB247A671E9F-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D9EF3DE9-DE5B-42C7-96EC-FB247A671E9F-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D9EF3DE9-DE5B-42C7-96EC-FB247A671E9F-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D9EF3DE9-DE5B-42C7-96EC-FB247A671E9F-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/D9EF3DE9-DE5B-42C7-96EC-FB247A671E9F-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br />對比上一代 NOAH，豐田 ALL NEW NOAH 由引擎、底盤、波箱、油耗都作出全面升級。搭配 2 公升直列式四汽缸雙頂凸輪軸 16 氣閥 VVT-i 引擎（M20A-FKS）及 10 前速 DirectShift 無段變速波箱，輸出最大馬力達 170 匹及 202Nm 最大扭力，平均油耗表現為 14.6 km / L (J-WLTC 制式)，比上一代提升 10-15%。這也是 MPV 車系首次改用豐田新世代造車工藝的 TNGA（Toyota New Global Architecture）GA-C MPV 專屬底盤，低重心設計、剛性強化、輕量化車身等各方面大大提升駕駛安全性、穩定性及操控樂趣。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/7D2FABAF-BC83-4909-AEF6-61066A5AB91C-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/7D2FABAF-BC83-4909-AEF6-61066A5AB91C-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/7D2FABAF-BC83-4909-AEF6-61066A5AB91C-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/7D2FABAF-BC83-4909-AEF6-61066A5AB91C-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/7D2FABAF-BC83-4909-AEF6-61066A5AB91C-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/7D2FABAF-BC83-4909-AEF6-61066A5AB91C-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/7D2FABAF-BC83-4909-AEF6-61066A5AB91C-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/31E13D7E-9992-4088-8AEC-22C18BDD41EA-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/31E13D7E-9992-4088-8AEC-22C18BDD41EA-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/31E13D7E-9992-4088-8AEC-22C18BDD41EA-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/31E13D7E-9992-4088-8AEC-22C18BDD41EA-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/31E13D7E-9992-4088-8AEC-22C18BDD41EA-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/31E13D7E-9992-4088-8AEC-22C18BDD41EA-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/31E13D7E-9992-4088-8AEC-22C18BDD41EA-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E967A8E0-FFDC-4FB0-AD60-EAFE2C19A591-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E967A8E0-FFDC-4FB0-AD60-EAFE2C19A591-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E967A8E0-FFDC-4FB0-AD60-EAFE2C19A591-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E967A8E0-FFDC-4FB0-AD60-EAFE2C19A591-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E967A8E0-FFDC-4FB0-AD60-EAFE2C19A591-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E967A8E0-FFDC-4FB0-AD60-EAFE2C19A591-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/E967A8E0-FFDC-4FB0-AD60-EAFE2C19A591-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1087938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6FE18BF4-D45B-4CC2-BC63-CE617DECD7A1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6FE18BF4-D45B-4CC2-BC63-CE617DECD7A1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6FE18BF4-D45B-4CC2-BC63-CE617DECD7A1-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6FE18BF4-D45B-4CC2-BC63-CE617DECD7A1-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6FE18BF4-D45B-4CC2-BC63-CE617DECD7A1-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6FE18BF4-D45B-4CC2-BC63-CE617DECD7A1-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/6FE18BF4-D45B-4CC2-BC63-CE617DECD7A1-scaled.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">另外，豐田 ALL NEW NOAH 首次為車系導入同級獨有 TOYOTA SAFETY SENSETM 3.0（TSS）第三代主動式安全系統，可主動偵測路況，輔助駕駛者判斷道路安全情況。全車備有 10 個安全氣袋及泊車防碰撞輔助系統（Parking Support Brake），為家人提供出行的最強防護網。當中的行車安全系統包括：預警式防護系統附自動煞車輔助（Pre-Collision System）、雷達感應式車距巡航定速系統（Dynamic Radar Cruise Control）、線道追蹤輔助系統 （Lane Tracing Assist）及智慧型高燈自動切換系統（AutomaticHigh-Beam）。</span></p>